{"tid":841924,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【昔日拍檔合體】阿諾拍《未來戰士6》 賀元祖女主角蓮達咸美頓牛一","createTime":"2018-09-30T01:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T03:29:32.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c48b36b5fe9a85b2742c22283cb9bf4fbda5a947","tid":841924,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180927/large/1538020751_e1ad.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180927%2Flarge%2F1538020751_e1ad.jpg&d=CMZvBETLpSXbKaXFH7%2BYuZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7fdbfb2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180927/large/1538020751_e1ad.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n荷李活大隻佬影星阿諾舒華辛力加（Arnold Schwarzenegger），今年7月已經71歲生日，佢嘅代表作《未來戰士》（Terminator）系列認真夠晒經典，當中呢個系列嘅元祖女主角蓮達咸美頓（Linda Hamilton），同阿諾都可算話係最佳拍檔，二人就齊齊回歸拍攝明年上映嘅《未來戰士》第六集。<br />\n昨日9月26日係蓮達咸美頓嘅62歲生日，阿諾於社交網賀好拍檔生日，公開二人於片場嘅煙韌合照，仲對比當年大家年青時嘅舊相，阿諾留言話：「我其中一個最喜愛的合作演員，一個真正厲害角色、一個很棒的人。」《未來戰士6》暫定明年夏天上映。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180927/large/1538020801_985e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180927%2Flarge%2F1538020801_985e.jpg&h=81f19fd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a0d0e513cd0e325d37e33ed2706c93d666de4a0","tid":841924,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:04:23.000Z","msg":"宜家荷里活係咪剩番翻炒同英雄電影<br />\n近呢年都無乜聽過有d好睇既原創電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b977278f6f534e63b37e3f72b60d01483a8a6dc2","tid":841924,"uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a0d0e513cd0e325d37e33ed2706c93d666de4a0","tid":841924,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:04:23.000Z","msg":"宜家荷里活係咪剩番翻炒同英雄電影<br />\n近呢年都無乜聽過有d好睇既原創電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}